tras/cdfd8bb64126dd2e9b2ab8f05b78e58d.webm?t=1651607437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897860/extras/cdfd8bb64126dd2e9b2ab8f05b78e58d.mp4?t=1651607437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• Find Spell Scrolls to learn powerful spells<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897860/extras/c023709bd64ca19708bf3a3b01053b52.poster.avif?t=1651607437\" width=612 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897860/extras/c023709bd64ca19708bf3a3b01053b52.webm?t=1651607437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897860/extras/c023709bd64ca19708bf3a3b01053b52.mp4?t=1651607437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• Return to camp between runs to craft new gear and items, cook food, visit the Merchant to trade, and upgrade your character at the Soul Forge<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897860/extras/b28101cab49cd9d5e069eb4c365f8074.poster.avif?t=1651607437\" width=612 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897860/extras/b28101cab49cd9d5e069eb4c365f8074.webm?t=1651607437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897860/extras/b28101cab49cd9d5e069eb4c365f8074.mp4?t=1651607437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• Immersive, original score",
